  "title": "Chase Padgett: How To Play Guitar (Poorly)",
  "description": "In this hilariously heartfelt musical memoir, Chase Padgett (6 Guitars, Nashville Hurricane) turns his lifelong guitar obsession into a soul-baring journey through music, missteps, and memory. From cringe-worthy teenage jazz band gigs to blistering solos and father-son reckonings, it’s part stand-up, part concert, and all heart. ★★★★★ “A deft actor and virtuoso guitar player” – CBC",
